title: Hard.Enduro.2012.Le.Tonquet.FUEL.720P.h264.English
description:
We look forward to some of the roughest, toughest races of the year including The Tough One, Hell's Gate, Erzberg Rodeo, Red Bull Romaniacs and Red Bull Sea to Sky. Featuring Graham Jarvis, Jonny Walker, Dougie Lampkin and a host of top riders.

The epic L'Enduropale du Touquet, created by the same man that created the Dakar Rally, is held in Northern France and features more than 1000 enduro riders, sand racing and moto x riders. This year see the world's first enduro on the frozen beaches of northern France.
